m_szDocSumamry: News:Fuel Efficiency News relating to Fuel Efficiency . 2015 Featured : Fuel Efficiency > GEET > GEET inventor, Paul Pantone, has passed away - World-renowned inventor, Paul Pantone, passed away this morning after suffering from a long illness. The simple version of his GEET (pre-heating incoming fuel with outgoing exhaust), improving mileage by 5-30%) has been replicated by tens of thousands; but his plasma effect (7x), which requires keen precision, still evades most researchers, but not all. (PESN; December 14, 2015) Featured : Fuel Efficiency > Hydroxy > Best > FOR SALE: DYNO Lab Results f
